sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Service<br/>(lmes-operator)
    participant Job as LMEval Job Container<br/>UID: 65532
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Model as Model Inference Service<br/>(KServe/vLLM)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PVC as PVC Model Cache<br/>Filesystem
    participant Output as Output Directory<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 1: Local Model Evaluation

    Operator->>Job: Creates K8s Job<br/>with container image
    Job->>HFHub: Download model, datasets, tokenizer<br/>GET HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>Job: Model weights + datasets
    Job->>Job: Load model (PyTorch in-process)<br/>Run evaluation tasks
    Job->>Job: Compute metrics<br/>(bundled offline metrics)
    Job->>Output: Write structured results<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 2: Remote Model Evaluation (Served Model)

    Operator->>Job: Creates K8s Job<br/>with container image
    Job->>HFHub: Download evaluation datasets<br/>GET HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>Job: Datasets + tokenizer
    Job->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (configurable)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Model-->>Job: Model predictions
    Job->>Job: Compute evaluation metrics
    Job->>Output: Write structured results<br/>Filesystem

    Note over Operator,Output: Flow 3: Disconnected/Air-Gapped Evaluation

    Operator->>Job: Creates K8s Job<br/>with container image
    Job->>PVC: Load model from cache<br/>Filesystem (no network)
    PVC-->>Job: Cached model weights
    Job->>Job: Load bundled metrics<br/>from container (metrics/)
    Job->>Job: Run evaluation tasks<br/>using local data
    Job->>Output: Write structured results<br/>Filesystem
